---
const install = 'cargo install sopsy';
// Each terminal line gets an incremental reveal delay.
const lines = [
  { c: 'prompt', t: 'sopsy init' },
  { c: 'cmt', t: '  ◇ checking toolchain …' },
  { c: 'ok', t: '  ✔ sops 3.9.4   ✔ age 1.2.1   ✔ age-plugin-se   ✔ git' },
  { c: 'cmt', t: '  ◇ generating Secure Enclave identity (Touch ID) …' },
  { c: 'key', t: '  ➜ public recipient  age1se1qg8vw9k2…  ← safe to share' },
  { c: 'info', t: '  ◇ writing repo files …' },
  { c: 'ok', t: '  ✔ .sops.yaml  ✔ .env.example  ✔ .env.encrypted' },
  { c: 'ok', t: '  ✔ .gitignore  ✔ .sopsy.yml' },
  { c: 'warn', t: '  ⚠ no break-glass key yet — add one before you ship' },
  { c: 'ok', t: '  ✔ repository bootstrapped in 4.2s' },
];
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow hero__kicker" data-reveal>A Rust CLI for SOPS · age · Secure Enclave</p>

    <h1 data-reveal>
      The missing <span class="swap">developer experience</span> for <em>SOPS</em>.
    </h1>

    <div class="hero__cols">
      <div data-reveal>
        <p class="hero__sub">
          <b>sopsy</b> makes it delightful to keep encrypted secrets in Git. It bootstraps a
          repo in minutes, mints hardware-backed identities in the macOS Secure Enclave, manages
          your team's recipients, and ships a CI gate that fails the build the second a plaintext
          secret sneaks in.
        </p>

        <div class="hero__actions">
          <div class="copyfield">
            <span class="sigil">$</span>
            <span>{install}</span>
            <button data-copy={install} aria-label="Copy install command">copy</button>
          </div>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="#quickstart">Quick start ↓</a>
        </div>

        <p class="hero__note">
          <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Doesn't replace SOPS — it makes SOPS delightful. Same engine, better defaults.
        </p>

        <div class="badges" aria-label="Project badges">
          <span class="badge">crate <b>v1</b></span>
          <span class="badge">CI <b class="lime">passing</b></span>
          <span class="badge">license <b>MIT / Apache-2.0</b></span>
          <span class="badge">🍎 <b>Apple Silicon</b></span>
          <span class="badge">key <b>never leaves the chip</b></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div data-reveal>
        <div class="terminal" role="img" aria-label="Terminal showing 'sopsy init' bootstrapping a repository">
        <div class="terminal__bar">
          <div class="terminal__dots"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
          <span class="terminal__title">~/my-app — sopsy</span>
        </div>
        <div class="terminal__body reveal-lines">
          {lines.map((l, i) => (
            <span class={`ln ${l.c}`} style={`animation-delay:${i * 220 + 200}ms`}>{l.t}</span>
          ))}
          <span class="ln prompt cursor" style={`animation-delay:${lines.length * 220 + 300}ms`}></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
